</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="so-small" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#so-small" aria-hidden="true">#</a> so small</h3>
<p>如此之小</p>
<div class="language-json line-numbers-mode" data-ext="json"><pre v-pre class="language-json"><code>some of which are so small <span class="token comment">// 其中一些是如此之小</span>

<span class="token comment">// “Some of which”是一个短语，通常用于连接两个句子或段落，表示其中一部分与另一部分有关联或相似。在这个短语中，“some”是不定代词，意思是“一些”，“of”是介词，“which”是关系代词，用来引导定语从句。</span>

