</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="known-as" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#known-as" aria-hidden="true">#</a> known as</h3>
<p>被称为</p>
<div class="language-json line-numbers-mode" data-ext="json"><pre v-pre class="language-json"><code><span class="token comment">// “Known as”是一个常用的英语短语，意思是“被称为”或“被认为是”。它通常用于介绍某人或某事的别名或绰号。例如：</span>
The city is known as the <span class="token string">"City of Lights"</span> because of its beautiful夜景.（这座城市因其美丽的夜景而被称为“光之城”。）
