<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// “Have serious reason”是一个常用的英语短语，意思是“有严肃的原因”或“有严重的理由”。它通常用于表示某个人或某个团体有充分的理由来做某件事情。例如：</span>
<span class="token class-name">We</span> have serious reason <span class="token keyword">to</span> <span class="token namespace">believe</span> that he is guilty<span class="token punctuation">.</span>（我们有充分的理由相信他有罪。）
<span class="token class-name">She</span> has serious reason <span class="token keyword">to</span> <span class="token namespace">suspect</span> that he is cheating on her<span class="token punctuation">.</span>（她有充分的理由怀疑他对她不忠。）
<span class="token class-name">They</span> have serious reason <span class="token keyword">to</span> <span class="token namespace">fear</span> that the company will go bankrupt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>（他们有充分的理由担心公司会破产。）
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="are-like-that" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#are-like-that" aria-hidden="true">#</a> are like that</h3>
